# Docs (embargoed until NeurIPS 2026 submission)
/docs

# Specific docs that are NOT embargoed and should be tracked.
# Add new entries here individually — never add "!/docs/papers/" or
# similar broad un-ignores, as that would expose the embargoed
# cubemind_iravenx_neurips2026.{md,tex,pdf} files.
#
# To un-ignore a file inside docs/, you need to un-ignore each parent
# directory first, then re-ignore everything inside it, then explicitly
# allow the file. Pattern:
#   !/docs/
#   /docs/*
#   !/docs/papers/
#   /docs/papers/*
#   !/docs/papers/MY_FILE.md
#
# Below is the minimal set for the LM training paper:
!/docs/
/docs/*
!/docs/papers/
/docs/papers/*
!/docs/papers/cubemind_lm_h200_training.md

